textBox.richText: Winter Park did another “Jane Look-a-like” contest for Jane’s Birthday. Alli almost got the Mayor to judge, but instead, he decided to enter it himself. Alli and Caitlin both dressed up, and they convinced Miles and James to be their “Miners”. I mostly “drilled” for the day...that pole-drag thing that Tom showed me Wednesday works wonders. I *think* I’m getting faster....and more confident. :)
